data.description: Secluded Log Cabin Retreat with Tranquil Creek - Perfect for Airbnb and Outdoor Enthusiasts Welcome to your dream retreat! Nestled in the heart of nature, this enchanting log cabin offers the ultimate getaway, boasting a serene creek running alongside the property. This hidden gem is perfect for those seeking a peaceful escape or an incredible investment opportunity on Airbnb. The soothing sounds of the babbling creek are the soundtrack to your stay, providing the perfect backdrop for relaxation and outdoor adventures. With a spacious yard, there's ample room for fun and games. Set up a fire pit for s'mores under the stars, challenge friends to a game of volleyball, or try your hand at horseshoes. There's no limit to the fun you can have. A 20 x 32 structure equipped with power and water, this space is versatile and ready for your imagination. Whether you want to convert it into a guest house, a workshop, or something entirely unique, the possibilities are endless. A brand new Generac generator ensures you'll never be left in the dark, providing peace of mind for you and your guests. A new well on the property delivers over 150 gallons of pure, clean water per minute, offering an ample and reliable source for all your needs. Enjoy the sights and sounds of nature from the comfort of a spacious screened porch that wraps around the cabin. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or watching the sun set, this feature is an absolute must for relaxation. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise that offers endless possibilities. Whether you're looking to invest in a profitable Airbnb property or simply seeking a peaceful haven, this log cabin is the perfect choice. Book your viewing today and let your dreams become a reality!
